when i update a piece of data, singlerecord performs the following checks:
1. filter contacts that have been added to the unsubscribe-list
2.a counts every sms in the list of contacts to be notified
2.b checks if owner has balance in his budget for all sms notifications (has-balance)
3. sends notifications to Queue
4.a if a message is in Queue, and there is NO past notification prior to 24 hours, send notifications
4.b else keep in Queue until 24 hours from last notification

